<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 04 at 3:29AM EST  by NWS Raleigh</headline>
<description>...Areas of Black Ice Are Possible Early This Morning...
Any lingering areas of snow, slush and runoff on roadways,
sidewalks, and parking lots will freeze through daybreak.
Black ice is difficult to see. Use caution if traveling or walking
this morning as slippery conditions are possible.</description>
